text: Georges Garreau (20 September 1902 - 21 June 1986) was a French diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1986 deaths Category:French male divers Category:Olympic divers of France Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Paris
